    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both of which have been recently calibrated for optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Equipped with Bilstein dampers and cross-drilled rotors, this M3 offers precise turn-in and consistent thermal management during spirited driving. A well-sorted example for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
