    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained example of automotive excellence that perfectly balances performance with daily usability. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serves as a testament to responsible ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the front valence consistent with careful highway use. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with ample tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary featuring supple leather seating with no punctures or significant bolster wear. Every technological feature, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as the manufacturer intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with full synthetic oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and the engine provides smooth, consistent power without any hesitations or unusual noises. I have compiled a comprehensive folder of service receipts to pass along to the next owner, ensuring total peace of mind. While it shows the gentle character of a car that has been enjoyed, it remains a reliable, high-quality driver that presents beautifully in any setting.",
      "price": 34800.0,
